===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Kabu (Masters)}}
Kabu forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Centiskorch}}, {{p|Torkoal}}, {{p|Ninetales}}, and {{p|Camerupt}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Centiskorch is capable of [[Gigantamax]]ing, while his Camerupt is capable of [[Dynamax]]ing. Kabu became a playable sync pair on June 16, 2024.

